## Checklist

- [ ] `<title>` unique, under 60 chars
- [ ] `meta description` under 160 chars
- [ ] `canonical` on duplicate-content pages
- [ ] `robots` not accidentally `noindex`
- [ ] OG: `og:title`, `og:description`, `og:image`, `og:url`, `og:type`
- [ ] Twitter: `twitter:card`, `twitter:title`, `twitter:description`, `twitter:image`
- [ ] JSON-LD with correct schema type
- [ ] All `<img>` have meaningful `alt`
- [ ] `next/image` used in Next.js
- [ ] `sitemap.xml` linked in `robots.txt`
- [ ] `robots.txt` not blocking public routes
- [ ] hreflang on every locale (if i18n)
- [ ] Page 1 canonical clean (if paginated)
